      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Iterative solver residuals monitored to convergence tolerance of 1e-6; force-displacement equilibrium checked at each load step. No divergence or spurious oscillations observed across all 11 model instances."
