    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency in Test conditions (achieved 2, required 3) is acknowledged; the assessment team determined that the remaining factor evidence, combined with multi-laboratory replication across N=11 constructs, provides sufficient overall credibility for Medium model risk at the assurance level required. Decision recorded as Accepted with noted limitation on test condition coverage.",
